{"title":"等您，我的友人","authors":["木斧"],"dates":[{"year":1990,"month":5,"day":24}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"等您，我的友人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"木斧"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"等您，我的友人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"像我的主人在您家里借宿一样"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我熟悉了东京的列车表"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我听惯了那亲切的声音"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“空呢女哇”“阿甲呷朵”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我便猛然坐起"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"记起了一段友情"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"友情是不老的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我不问您的年龄"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我便记起了美妙的诗吟"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"等你，在黄昏后"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"夕阳吻着飘动的窗帘"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"窗帘中飘出一个身影，是您"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"曾经用樱红抚过的友情"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"漂洋过海来了吗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"夜夜同我促膝谈心"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"等您，在黎明"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看见和煦的春风"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你会说，昨夜我睡得很好"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"像回到了我的家中一样"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"正如我的主人在您家里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"对您说过的话一样"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"您的欢乐成了我的欢乐"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们便成了亲密的友人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"等您，我在中国"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"等候日本的友人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不管你来与不来"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你引发了我的诗兴"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我把广岛和成都的太阳"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"重叠在一个圆圈上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"叠出一个滚烫的心"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}